Thruk Developer integrates Thruks current git verion into OMD

### WARNING ###
this step cannot be reverted by script, so only do this in test sites!


All steps have to be done as site user

1. clone thruk from github

   %> cd ~/local/share && git clone git://github.com/sni/Thruk.git

2. clone omd utils from github

   %> cd ~/local/share && git clone git://github.com/sni/omd_utils.git

3. run the install script

   %> ~/local/share/omd_utils/thruk_developer/install.sh ~/local/share/Thruk

4. start omd

   %> omd start
